    <title>淺談一下 SmartPtr</title>
    <url>/2022/06/11/code/cpp/loki/SmartPtr/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>關於智能指針，這是一個十分誘人的主題，至少對於C++。對於C++而言，可以這麽説， smart pointers是最普及、最複雜、最强大的工具：其吸引人的地方在於，它涉及語法和語義上的很多議題。</p>
<p>smart pointers 是一種C++對象，它提供<code>operator-&gt;</code>和<strong>unary</strong> <code>operator*</code>， 以此模擬一般指針（simple pointers）的行爲。除了提供指針的語法和語義，smart pointers 通常會在底層完成很多有用的工作（例如内存管理或鎖定操作），這麽以來，對於smart pointers所指對象的生命周期，應用程序就不必特意管理。</p>
<span id="more"></span>


<figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption><span>Import Demo</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// &#123;\% include_code AllowConversion lang:cpp from:56 to:59 cpp/loki/SmartPtr.cpp \%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Smart-Pointers-基礎"><a href="#Smart-Pointers-基礎" class="headerlink" title="Smart Pointers 基礎"></a>Smart Pointers 基礎</h2><p>什麽是smart pointer?它是一個C++ class，在語法和某些語義上模擬一般指針，但提供更多功能。由於smart pointers指向“類型各異”之對象，所以他們勢必擁有大量共通代碼，所以現有的高質量smart pointers幾乎都以template完成，template參數為被指物（pointee）之型別，正如以下所見：</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><figcaption><span>AllowConversion</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">T</span>&gt; <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmartPtr</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">explicit</span> <span class="title">SmartPtr</span><span class="params">(T* pointee)</span>: pointee_(pointee);</span></span><br><span class="line">    SmartPtr&amp; <span class="keyword">operator</span>=(<span class="type">const</span> SmartPtr&amp; other);</span><br><span class="line">    ~<span class="built_in">SmartPtr</span>();</span><br><span class="line marked">    T&amp; <span class="keyword">operator</span>*() <span class="type">const</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> *pointee_;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line marked">    T* <span class="keyword">operator</span>-&gt;() <span class="type">const</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> pointee_;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    T* pointee_;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="關於解構的-Policy"><a href="#關於解構的-Policy" class="headerlink" title="關於解構的 Policy"></a>關於解構的 Policy</h2><h3 id="OwnerPolicy"><a href="#OwnerPolicy" class="headerlink" title="OwnerPolicy"></a>OwnerPolicy</h3><h4 id="RefCounted"><a href="#RefCounted" class="headerlink" title="RefCounted"></a>RefCounted</h4><p>引用計數法，此法追蹤</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><figcaption><span>RefCounted</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">P</span>&gt; <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">RefCounted</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line marked">    <span class="type">unsigned</span> <span class="type">int</span>* pCount_;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">protected</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">RefCounted</span>(): <span class="built_in">pCount_</span>(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">unsigned</span> <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)) &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">IsUnique</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123; <span class="keyword">return</span> *pCount_ == <span class="number">1</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">P <span class="title">Clone</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> P&amp; val)</span> </span>&#123; ++*pCount_; <span class="keyword">return</span> val; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">Release</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> P&amp;)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="keyword">if</span> (!--*pCount_) <span class="keyword">delete</span> pCount_; <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">static</span> <span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">hello</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123; std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello RefCounted!\n&quot;</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">enum</span> &#123; destructiveCopy = <span class="literal">false</span> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



]]></content>
